{"tid":1551530,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［極重要］今日請大家一定要和理非！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:53:15.000Z","uid":193485,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"14d93afae520558124ef9d95b50e19c045e6158b","tid":1551530,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"港共政府多番打壓遊行活動，<br />\n唯獨今日香港公安就批出不反對通知書，背後絕對有機會派出卧底偽裝示威者，乘機作亂搞事，例如塗鴉或破壞美領、燒美國國旗、唱美國國歌時大聲喧嘩等，以抹黑香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n所以，請大家今日一定要克制，如望到有任何不合適不合理不合作，請幫忙制止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美領見！"},{"pid":"9b5fbd2892408e4a7222450f33a46fc5848aea7f","tid":1551530,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"推到俾全世界見到"},{"pid":"df9f2470290d2d12082781f86e506a13e203b854","tid":1551530,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清理地上/垃圾桶國旗 <br />\n阻止人向美領射laser<br />\n邊個衝美領老閪都拉住佢</span></span></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fc27a5288d59d5356c3fc787d124c7c2811a9fbc","tid":1551530,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375aec6ed2ef21b5a1c87f878d367d2930e3fc01","tid":1551530,"uid":74929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16DxAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16DxAR.jpg&h=6b663e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1mTkZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1mTkZ7.jpg&h=106f1e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/08/121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F08%2F121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg&h=0ace8822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Gvdmuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Gvdmuh.jpg&h=88cf1465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>美國國歌唔同大陸國歌唔需要一定跟著唱 大部份場合只有一個領唱者</ins> <br />\n<br />\n唔識唱嘅話單手放心口就得<br />\n唔想放喺心口嘅話面向國旗都可<br />\n<br />\n記得除帽 口罩要帶保護返自己<br />\n美國佬好隨和其實着咩都冇所謂<br />\n<ins>最緊要有人到有心最重要</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>今日大家美國領事館見</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n緊急9月8號 weconnect美國重要日子 注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551454\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff9ec624211a9e75f2f19ddefc1ab02b9cc65c4a","tid":1551530,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42fbe3d2e0ed1213dab1f4627335caed99fa2c3","tid":1551530,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱fuck the popo <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱毅進仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱今天我 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日係唱The Star-Spangled Banner</span>🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一定一定要係國際媒體面前一齊全民大合唱啊<br />\n點都要唱到第一段啊！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<del>因為全首太長</del><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\nOh, say can you see by the dawn's early light<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars thru the perilous fight,<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night that our flag was still there.<br />\nOh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫英文口號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Five demands Not one less</span><br />\n香港警察 知法犯法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Hong Kong Police breaking the peace</span><br />\n與港同在 促成人權法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Stand with Hong Kong, pass the democracy act</span><br />\n為自由抗爭 制度已失衡<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Fight for freedom, no faith in the systems</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應對記者資料</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂][行動] 9月8點應對外國記者+3首歌歌詞+資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551469\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d341dd2f4b9972995d0a60f10b622e96ad0f3b14","tid":1551530,"uid":263366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:59:32.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1705116a7023b181029dfb9ab0f57309de6f30","tid":1551530,"uid":247708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c355d94d600a4ca70a899bc99ac483688d60b1cc","tid":1551530,"uid":253148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2db1f4ed642a1e20a415740459f388be51eca0d","tid":1551530,"uid":41512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"邊個衝擊邊個就係鬼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i